<li> &quot;We humbly asked Him to remove our shortcomings&quot;
&nbsp; &nbsp; <font size="-1">The <i>Big Book</i>, 3rd &amp; 4th editions, William G. Wilson, page 59.</font>
<li> <i>&quot;Let Go And Let God.&quot;</i>
