<a href="orange-funny_spirituality.html#Narcissistic" target="_blank">
Narcissistic Personality Disorder</a>, the signs of which Bill Wilson
prominently displayed.)
</font>
<p>
Also, the DSM-IV is the &quot;bible&quot; of psychiatrists, not &quot;medical doctors&quot;
or &quot;physicians&quot;.<br>

